data.description: Charming three bed two bath home available for sale in Ponchatoula! Conveniently located in proximity to interstate, hospital, and just a hop and a skip from Hammond or downtown Ponchatoula.  This home features vinyl flooring throughout home, and an HVAC system that is only two years old!  Home has wonderful yard space with tons of landscaping potential in front and rear of home.  Situated in a quaint neighborhood, this home also has covered parking and an outdoor storage space.  Schedule your viewing today!
